WEBVTT

00:12:59.141 --> 00:13:01.514
to remember, like,
the footnotes of history,

00:13:01.538 --> 00:13:06.918
which is that the dude who came up
with the phrase "sex chromosome,"

00:13:06.942 --> 00:13:10.545
actually was like, "Hey, everyone,
just remember, this is just,"

00:13:10.569 --> 00:13:12.820
and I quote, "a form of shorthand."

00:13:13.887 --> 00:13:16.020
We should not take it literally.

00:13:16.641 --> 00:13:17.799
Thank you.

00:13:17.823 --> 00:13:21.394
(Applause)